864
00:45:04.530 --> 00:45:06.560
The City Watch is fiercely loyal to him.

865
00:45:06.670 --> 00:45:10.470
- An army 2.000 strong.

866
00:45:06.670 --> 00:45:10.470
- An army you gave him. Otto.

867
00:45:10.540 --> 00:45:14.500
I named Daemon Master of Laws.

868
00:45:10.540 --> 00:45:14.500
