869
00:45:14.570 --> 00:45:17.040
As Master of Coin.

870
00:45:14.570 --> 00:45:17.040
you said he was a spendthrift

871
00:45:17.140 --> 00:45:18.630
that would beggar the realm.

872
00:45:18.710 --> 00:45:20.910
Putting Daemon in command

873
00:45:18.710 --> 00:45:20.910
