878
00:45:27.720 --> 00:45:28.880
Daemon is my brother.

879
00:45:29.920 --> 00:45:31.150
My blood.

880
00:45:32.090 --> 00:45:34.060
And he will have his place at my court.

881
00:45:34.160 --> 00:45:36.150
[Mellos] Let him keep his place

882
00:45:34.160 --> 00:45:36.150
at court. Your Grace.

883
00:45:36.230 --> 00:45:40.390
but if the gods should visit

884
00:45:36.230 --> 00:45:40.390
