885
00:45:40.500 --> 00:45:43.700
- either by design or by accident.

886
00:45:40.500 --> 00:45:43.700
- [sighs] "Design"?

887
00:45:44.240 --> 00:45:45.600
What are you saying?

888
00:45:45.710 --> 00:45:48.040
My brother would murder me.

889
00:45:45.710 --> 00:45:48.040
