890
00:45:49.740 --> 00:45:50.730
Are you?

891
00:45:52.610 --> 00:45:53.600
Please.

892
00:45:54.780 --> 00:45:58.440
Daemon has ambition. yes.

893
00:45:54.780 --> 00:45:58.440
but not for the throne.

894
00:45:58.550 --> 00:46:00.250
He lacks the patience for it.

895
00:46:00.350 --> 00:46:01.840
The gods have yet to make a man

896
00:46:01.920 --> 00:46:05.450
who lacks the patience

897
00:46:01.920 --> 00:46:05.450
for absolute power. Your Grace.

898
00:46:05.560 --> 00:46:09.550
[Mellos] Under such circumstances.

899
00:46:05.560 --> 00:46:09.550
it would not be an aberration

900
00:46:09.630 --> 00:46:12.220
for the King to name a successor.

901
00:46:12.300 --> 00:46:14.030
Well. who else would have a claim?

902
00:46:20.640 --> 00:46:22.800
The King's firstborn child.

903
00:46:22.910 --> 00:46:25.070
Rhaenyra? A girl?

904
00:46:26.780 --> 00:46:28.750
No queen has ever sat the Iron Throne.

905
00:46:28.810 --> 00:46:30.940
That is only by tradition

906
00:46:28.810 --> 00:46:30.940
and precedent. Lord Strong.

907
00:46:31.050 --> 00:46:33.250
If order and stability

908
00:46:31.050 --> 00:46:33.250
so concerns this council.

909
00:46:33.320 --> 00:46:37.150
then perhaps we shouldn't break

910
00:46:33.320 --> 00:46:37.150
100 years of it by naming a girl heir.

911
00:46:37.260 --> 00:46:40.990
Daemon would be a second Maegor.

912
00:46:37.260 --> 00:46:40.990
or worse.

913
00:46:41.090 --> 00:46:43.090
He is impulsive and violent.

914
00:46:43.800 --> 00:46:45.660
It is the duty of this council

915
00:46:45.770 --> 00:46:48.760
to protect the King

916
00:46:45.770 --> 00:46:48.760
and the realm from him.

917
00:46:50.140 --> 00:46:52.500
I'm sorry. Your Grace.

918
00:46:50.140 --> 00:46:52.500
but that is the truth as I see it.

919
00:46:52.610 --> 00:46:54.130
and I know that others here agree.

920
00:46:54.240 --> 00:46:58.180
I will not be made to choose

921
00:46:54.240 --> 00:46:58.180
between my brother and my daughter.

922
00:46:58.280 --> 00:47:00.110
[Corlys] You wouldn't have to.

923
00:46:58.280 --> 00:47:00.110
Your Grace.

924
00:47:00.180 --> 00:47:02.240
There are others who would have a claim.

925
00:47:02.320 --> 00:47:04.340
[laughs] Such as your wife. Lord Corlys?

926
00:47:04.450 --> 00:47:06.650
- "The Queen Who Never Was"?

927
00:47:04.450 --> 00:47:06.650
- Rhaenys was the only child

928
00:47:06.750 --> 00:47:07.910
of Jaehaerys' eldest son.

929
00:47:07.990 --> 00:47:09.980
She had a strong claim

930
00:47:07.990 --> 00:47:09.980
at the Great Council.

931
00:47:10.090 --> 00:47:12.020
and she already has a male heir.

932
00:47:12.120 --> 00:47:14.530
Just moments ago.

933
00:47:12.120 --> 00:47:14.530
