934
00:47:14.630 --> 00:47:16.600
If we cannot agree on an heir.

935
00:47:14.630 --> 00:47:16.600
then how can we expect--

936
00:47:16.660 --> 00:47:18.100
My wife and son are dead!

937
00:47:20.300 --> 00:47:24.830
I will not sit here and suffer crows

938
00:47:20.300 --> 00:47:24.830
that come to feast on their corpses!

939
00:47:40.390 --> 00:47:41.350
[sighs]

940
00:47:52.130 --> 00:47:54.620
[blows]

941
00:47:58.700 --> 00:48:00.330
Send a raven to Oldtown.

942
00:48:00.810 --> 00:48:02.140
Straight away.

943
00:48:04.880 --> 00:48:05.970
My lady.

944
00:48:11.320 --> 00:48:13.010
[breath trembling]

945
00:48:15.320 --> 00:48:16.550
[Alicent crying]

946
00:48:16.660 --> 00:48:17.680
[Otto] My darling.

947
00:48:23.160 --> 00:48:24.060
[kisses]

948
00:48:27.230 --> 00:48:28.360
How's Rhaenyra?

949
00:48:31.440 --> 00:48:32.600
She lost her mother.

950
00:48:34.670 --> 00:48:36.770
The Queen was well-loved by all.

951
00:48:39.380 --> 00:48:42.580
I found myself thinking

952
00:48:39.380 --> 00:48:42.580
