953
00:48:49.190 --> 00:48:51.780
- How is His Grace?

954
00:48:49.190 --> 00:48:51.780
- [Otto] Very low.

955
00:48:53.260 --> 00:48:55.130
Which is why I sent for you.

956
00:49:00.430 --> 00:49:02.030
I thought you might go to him.

957
00:49:03.200 --> 00:49:04.260
