958
00:49:07.310 --> 00:49:08.470
In his chambers?

959
00:49:15.210 --> 00:49:16.710
I wouldn't know what to say.

960
00:49:17.750 --> 00:49:18.880
Stop that.

961
00:49:20.920 --> 00:49:22.450
He'll be glad of a visitor.

962
00:49:31.100 --> 00:49:33.160
You might wear

963
00:49:31.100 --> 00:49:33.160
one of your mother's dresses.

964
00:49:56.490 --> 00:49:57.350
[sighs]

965
00:50:03.200 --> 00:50:04.460
[knock at door]

966
00:50:06.430 --> 00:50:07.300
