967
00:50:10.270 --> 00:50:12.860
The Lady Alicent Hightower. Your Grace.

968
00:50:18.610 --> 00:50:20.310
[Viserys I] What is it. Alicent?

969
00:50:20.380 --> 00:50:22.510
I thought I might come

970
00:50:20.380 --> 00:50:22.510
and look in on you. Your Grace.

971
00:50:24.850 --> 00:50:26.280
I brought a book.

972
00:50:28.550 --> 00:50:30.110
That's very kind. thank you.

973
00:50:35.630 --> 00:50:37.120
It's a favorite of mine.

974
00:50:38.030 --> 00:50:40.660
I do know how passionate

975
00:50:38.030 --> 00:50:40.660
you are for the histories.

976
00:50:41.970 --> 00:50:43.960
Yes. I am.

977
00:51:01.590 --> 00:51:02.650
When my mother died.

978
00:51:04.590 --> 00:51:06.350
people only ever spoke to me in riddles.

979
00:51:08.730 --> 00:51:10.920
All I wanted was for someone

980
00:51:08.730 --> 00:51:10.920
to say that they were sorry

981
00:51:11.030 --> 00:51:12.050
for what happened to me.

982
00:51:16.770 --> 00:51:18.100
I'm very sorry. Your Grace.

983
00:51:21.170 --> 00:51:22.400
[sighs]

984
00:51:29.280 --> 00:51:30.770
[somber music playing]

985
00:51:30.880 --> 00:51:34.080
[people moaning in pleasure]

986
00:51:50.970 --> 00:51:53.440
- [people cheering]

987
00:51:50.970 --> 00:51:53.440
- [drums beating]

988
00:52:06.590 --> 00:52:07.580
Thank you.

989
00:52:09.760 --> 00:52:12.120
The King's sole heir once again.

990
00:52:13.990 --> 00:52:16.790
Might we drink to our future?

991
00:52:16.900 --> 00:52:18.230
[thudding]

992
00:52:18.300 --> 00:52:19.990
Quiet!

993
00:52:20.100 --> 00:52:22.730
Your Prince will speak!

994
00:52:25.800 --> 00:52:27.800
Silence!

995
00:52:33.680 --> 00:52:35.740
[Otto] Before we begin. Your Grace.

996
00:52:35.810 --> 00:52:39.810
I have a report

997
00:52:35.810 --> 00:52:39.810
I feel compelled to share.

998
00:52:41.920 --> 00:52:43.120
Last night.

999
00:52:43.960 --> 00:52:46.620
Prince Daemon bought out

1000
00:52:43.960 --> 00:52:46.620
one of the pleasure houses

1001
00:52:46.690 --> 00:52:48.320
on the Street of Silk.

1002
00:52:49.330 --> 00:52:52.590
to entertain officers of the City Watch

1003
00:52:52.670 --> 00:52:54.290
and other friends of his.

1004
00:52:58.000 --> 00:53:00.170
King and Council

1005
00:52:58.000 --> 00:53:00.170
have long rued my position

1006
00:53:00.270 --> 00:53:02.370
as next in line for the throne.

1007
00:53:02.470 --> 00:53:03.640
[indistinct chatter]

1008
00:53:03.710 --> 00:53:06.270
[Prince Daemon] But dream and pray

1009
00:53:03.710 --> 00:53:06.270
as they all might.

1010
00:53:06.350 --> 00:53:09.940
- it seems I'm not so easily replaced.

1011
00:53:06.350 --> 00:53:09.940
- [all cheering]

1012
00:53:11.550 --> 00:53:14.320
The gods give

1013
00:53:11.550 --> 00:53:14.320
just as the gods take away.

1014
00:53:14.390 --> 00:53:16.290
[Otto] He toasted Prince Baelon.

1015
00:53:16.360 --> 00:53:17.520
To the King's son.

1016
00:53:18.560 --> 00:53:19.990
[Otto] Styling him

1017
00:53:21.330 --> 00:53:23.890
"The Heir for a Day."

1018
00:53:30.740 --> 00:53:34.670
I corroborated this report

1019
00:53:30.740 --> 00:53:34.670
with three separate witnesses.

1020
00:53:34.740 --> 00:53:38.580
The evening was.

1021
00:53:34.740 --> 00:53:38.580
by all accounts. a celebration.

1022
00:53:41.150 --> 00:53:43.640
[Prince Daemon] You cut the image

1023
00:53:41.150 --> 00:53:43.640
of the conqueror. brother.

1024
00:53:45.580 --> 00:53:46.880
Did you say it?

1025
00:53:49.190 --> 00:53:50.520
I don't know what you mean.

1026
00:53:50.590 --> 00:53:52.020
[Viserys I] You will address me

1027
00:53:50.590 --> 00:53:52.020
as "Your Grace."

1028
00:53:52.090 --> 00:53:55.430
or I will have my Kingsguard

1029
00:53:52.090 --> 00:53:55.430
cut out your tongue.

1030
00:53:58.930 --> 00:54:03.370
"The Heir for a Day." Did you say it?

1031
00:54:12.850 --> 00:54:15.870
We must all mourn

1032
00:54:12.850 --> 00:54:15.870
in our own way. Your Grace.

1033
00:54:17.280 --> 00:54:20.680
My family has just been destroyed.

1034
00:54:21.750 --> 00:54:24.920
But instead of being

1035
00:54:21.750 --> 00:54:24.920
by my side. or Rhaenyra's.

1036
00:54:25.020 --> 00:54:27.720
you chose to celebrate your own rise!

1037
00:54:27.790 --> 00:54:30.520
Laughing with your whores

1038
00:54:27.790 --> 00:54:30.520
and your lickspittles!

1039
00:54:33.130 --> 00:54:36.230
You have no allies at court but me!

1040
00:54:36.300 --> 00:54:39.030
I have only ever defended you!

1041
00:54:39.100 --> 00:54:41.540
Yet everything I've given you.

1042
00:54:39.100 --> 00:54:41.540
