1043
00:54:41.610 --> 00:54:43.440
You've only ever tried to send me away.

1044
00:54:43.540 --> 00:54:46.240
To the Vale. to the City Watch.

1045
00:54:46.310 --> 00:54:48.280
anywhere but by your side.

1046
00:54:48.380 --> 00:54:50.410
Ten years you've been king.

1047
00:54:50.480 --> 00:54:53.610
and yet not once have you

1048
00:54:50.480 --> 00:54:53.610
