1049
00:54:53.720 --> 00:54:56.780
- Why would I do that?

1050
00:54:53.720 --> 00:54:56.780
- Because I'm your brother.

1051
00:54:57.820 --> 00:54:59.790
And the blood of the dragon runs thick.

1052
00:54:59.890 --> 00:55:01.880
Then why do you cut me so deeply?

1053
00:55:01.960 --> 00:55:04.950
I've only ever spoken the truth.

1054
00:55:01.960 --> 00:55:04.950
I see Otto Hightower for what he is.

1055
00:55:06.060 --> 00:55:07.460
[Viserys I] An unwavering

1056
00:55:06.060 --> 00:55:07.460
and loyal Hand?

1057
00:55:07.570 --> 00:55:08.470
A cunt.

1058
00:55:10.070 --> 00:55:12.060
A second son

1059
00:55:10.070 --> 00:55:12.060
who stands to inherit nothing

1060
00:55:12.140 --> 00:55:13.570
