1061
00:55:13.640 --> 00:55:15.730
Otto Hightower is a more honorable man

1062
00:55:15.810 --> 00:55:17.940
- than you could ever be.

1063
00:55:15.810 --> 00:55:17.940
- He doesn't protect you.

1064
00:55:18.010 --> 00:55:19.980
- I would.

1065
00:55:18.010 --> 00:55:19.980
- From what?

1066
00:55:20.080 --> 00:55:21.270
Yourself.

1067
00:55:24.980 --> 00:55:27.750
You're weak. Viserys.

1068
00:55:30.290 --> 00:55:31.780
And that council of leeches knows it.

1069
00:55:31.860 --> 00:55:33.850
They all prey on you for their own ends.

1070
00:55:38.800 --> 00:55:40.860
I have decided to name a new heir.

1071
00:55:40.970 --> 00:55:43.600
- I'm your heir.

1072
00:55:40.970 --> 00:55:43.600
- [Viserys I] Not anymore.

1073
00:55:44.100 --> 00:55:44.930
[ominous music playing]

1074
00:55:45.000 --> 00:55:48.630
You are to return to Runestone

1075
00:55:45.000 --> 00:55:48.630
and your lady wife at once.

1076
00:55:48.710 --> 00:55:50.800
and you are to do so without quarrel

1077
00:55:51.880 --> 00:55:53.870
by order of your King.

1078
00:56:08.830 --> 00:56:10.230
Your Grace.

1079
00:57:09.760 --> 00:57:10.950
Father.

1080
00:57:15.230 --> 00:57:17.060
Balerion was the last living creature

1081
00:57:17.130 --> 00:57:19.430
to have seen Old Valyria

1082
00:57:17.130 --> 00:57:19.430
before the Doom.

1083
00:57:22.430 --> 00:57:24.530
Its greatness and its flaws.

1084
00:57:25.070 --> 00:57:27.600
When you look at the dragons.

1085
00:57:25.070 --> 00:57:27.600
what do you see?

1086
00:57:27.710 --> 00:57:28.730
What?

1087
00:57:28.810 --> 00:57:31.970
You haven't spoken a word to me

1088
00:57:28.810 --> 00:57:31.970
since mother's funeral.

1089
00:57:32.080 --> 00:57:34.480
- and now you send your Kingsguard down.

1090
00:57:32.080 --> 00:57:34.480
- Answer me.

1091
00:57:37.550 --> 00:57:38.540
It's important.

1092
00:57:39.620 --> 00:57:41.050
What do you see?

1093
00:57:48.890 --> 00:57:51.490
- I suppose I see us.

1094
00:57:48.890 --> 00:57:51.490
- Tell me.

1095
00:57:52.600 --> 00:57:56.470
Everyone says Targaryens

1096
00:57:52.600 --> 00:57:56.470
are closer to gods than to men.

1097
00:57:56.570 --> 00:57:58.800
but they say that

1098
00:57:56.570 --> 00:57:58.800
because of our dragons.

1099
00:58:00.740 --> 00:58:03.300
Without them.

1100
00:58:00.740 --> 00:58:03.300
we're just like everyone else.

1101
00:58:05.910 --> 00:58:09.080
The idea that we control the dragons

1102
00:58:09.980 --> 00:58:11.610
is an illusion.

1103
00:58:13.320 --> 00:58:16.310
They're a power man should

1104
00:58:13.320 --> 00:58:16.310
never have trifled with.

1105
00:58:17.790 --> 00:58:20.160
One that brought Valyria its doom.

1106
00:58:20.260 --> 00:58:23.820
If we don't mind our own histories.

1107
00:58:20.260 --> 00:58:23.820
it will do the same to us.

1108
00:58:24.360 --> 00:58:26.590
Targaryen must understand

1109
00:58:24.360 --> 00:58:26.590
this to be King

1110
00:58:28.370 --> 00:58:29.360
or Queen.

1111
00:58:31.040 --> 00:58:33.700
[somber music playing]

1112
00:58:33.810 --> 00:58:35.430
I'm sorry. Rhaenyra.

1113
00:58:36.380 --> 00:58:39.350
I have wasted the years

1114
00:58:36.380 --> 00:58:39.350
since you were born

1115
00:58:39.440 --> 00:58:40.540
wanting for a son.

1116
00:58:53.030 --> 00:58:55.120
You are the very best of your mother.

1117
00:58:58.230 --> 00:59:00.390
And I believe it. I know she did.

1118
00:59:00.500 --> 00:59:02.830
that you could be a great ruling queen.

1119
00:59:02.900 --> 00:59:04.630
Daemon is your heir.

1120
00:59:06.240 --> 00:59:08.970
[Viserys I] Daemon was not made

1121
00:59:06.240 --> 00:59:08.970
to wear the crown.

1122
00:59:09.470 --> 00:59:11.030
But I believe that you were.

1123
00:59:12.140 --> 00:59:15.080
[man] Corlys of House Velaryon.

1124
00:59:15.180 --> 00:59:19.240
Lord of the Tides

1125
00:59:15.180 --> 00:59:19.240
and Master of Driftmark.

1126
00:59:19.350 --> 00:59:21.840
I. Corlys Velaryon.

1127
00:59:22.550 --> 00:59:25.720
Lord of the Tides

1128
00:59:22.550 --> 00:59:25.720
and Master of Driftmark.

1129
00:59:25.820 --> 00:59:27.880
promise to be faithful to King Viserys

1130
00:59:27.990 --> 00:59:30.830
and his named heir.

1131
00:59:27.990 --> 00:59:30.830
the Princess Rhaenyra.

1132
00:59:30.900 --> 00:59:32.090
I pledge fealty to them

1133
00:59:33.230 --> 00:59:35.170
and shall defend them

1134
00:59:33.230 --> 00:59:35.170
against all enemies

1135
00:59:35.230 --> 00:59:37.860
